Nvidia opens new tab hit $2 trillion in market value on Friday, riding on an insatiable demand for its chips that made the Silicon Valley firm the pioneer of the generative artificial intelligence boom. - @thesolution.ai 

The milestone followed another bumper revenue forecast from the chip designer that drove up its market value by $277 billion on Thursday - Wall Street’s largest one-day gain on record.

Its rapid ascent in the past year has led analysts to draw parallels to the picks and shovels providers during the gold rush of 1800s as Nvidia’s chips are used by almost all generative AI players from chatGPT-maker OpenAI to Google.

Nvidia’s shares +60%. Why you havent‘t missed the boat. 
Nvidia’s shares are up 60% this year, but if you think you missed the Nvidia boat, which I don’t think you have. Then this video is for you. 

I think Nvidia has untapped growth ahead of, because;
Firstly -  The majority of Nvidia’s revenue is from its data center division, as in it sells chips to big tech companies like Microsoft, Meta, Amazon and Alphabet. These tech giants are ordering more AI chips, to stay competitive and boost efficiency. 

Secondly- Nvidia’s CEO said, AI demand is surging across industries and nations – but currently its core clients are in tech. So this means, Nvidia’s at the tip point of scaling into other industries like healthcare and agriculture.

Thirdly - Nvidia’s H100 AI chips are now being shipped in under 3-4 months, instead of 8-11 months, meaning Nvidia’s is getting more immediate revenue and increasing productivity. Plus Nvidia will begin selling its new H200 chip next quarter. It has a higher price tag and quicker speeds and tech giants have already preordered it.

👉 台積電公告去年第四季獲利高於市場預期，並預估今年全年營收可望成長超過二成！同時預告三奈米製程去年下半年開始進入量產階段，預期今年營收成長將達3 倍以上，營收占比將從6% 大幅跳升至14-16%！

法說利多激勵台積電ADR大漲9.8%，台股期貨夜盤也隨之飆漲233點！Nvidia上漲1.8%，AMD也有將近1.6%漲幅，終於跟隨Nvidia腳步創下歷史新高了📈

🍎 另外在一堆華爾街投行都調降評等之際，美國銀行竟然逆勢發表看多Apple報告！並將評等從中性提高到買進，目標價也大幅拉高到225美元，距離目前股價大約還有二成左右漲幅！

Apple股價應聲大漲逾3%，帶動那斯達克100指數創下歷史新高，那斯達克指數大漲1.3%則是已經彌平新年以來跌幅，正式扭轉為2024全年上漲的情況👏
